      "title": "Two more deaths reported in fuel queues",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Two men who were waiting in a fuel queue in Kinniya have died today (July 22), Ada Derana correspondent says.",
        "One of the deceased, a 59-year-old was passed away while waiting in a queue in Kinniya while the other, 64, died in a queue at a filling station in Pelawatte."
      ],
